title: Dyno Run: Mitsubishi Lancer (2008-09 body) with a Takeda Short Ram Intake
description: This Mitsubishi Lancer nets +6 hp and +7 ft/lbs of torque when it gets dynoed with only the addition of a Takeda Short Ram Air Intake.
tags: Takeda Short Ram Intake, Short Ram Intake, Lancer Dyno

asset.title: Dyno: Mitsubishi Lancer (2008-09 body) with a Takeda Short Ram Intake
asset.description:
This Mitsubishi Lancer gets dynoed with a Takeda Short Ram Air Intake from AFE. The Lancer's only modification is the SRI and it nets +6 horsepower and +7 ft-lbs of torque. 

Find out how much power your vehicle can gain with a Takeda Intake by heading over to AutoAnything: http://www.autoanything.com/air-intakes/73A5155A0A0.aspx

View all air intake products here: http://www.autoanything.com/air-intakes/10A50208.aspx
